The paper deals with adaptive data analysis, which is a topic that falls under machine learning and statistics. The paper proposes new notions of natural analysts that interpolate between non-adaptive and fully adaptive cases. This suggests that the paper could be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
